finalPattern.pattern_name: Confession-style negative titles that conceal the target (e.g., “I’m Sorry…This [X] Sucks”) generate materially higher TPS by combining a taboo-feeling confession, a high-contrast negative verdict, and a curiosity gap from not naming the subject.

evidence.title: I'm Sorry...This New Artist Completely Sucks
